@startuml
title Cancel Booking Sequence Diagram

actor Customer
participant "WhatsApp Bot\n(src/bot.js)" as Bot
participant "Orders Store\n(src/orders.js)" as Orders

Customer -> Bot : Choose order and select Cancel
Bot --> Customer : Ask for cancellation confirmation
Customer -> Bot : Confirm Yes, cancel
Bot -> Orders : deleteOrder(id)
Orders --> Bot : deletion result
Bot --> Customer : Send cancellation confirmation

@enduml
